parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radiator can cause coolant to mix with transmission fluid, leading to transmission damage, loss of power, and potential accidents.
symptoms: Radiator fluid leakage
transmission slippage
loss of power
overheating
unusual noises
and difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure Due to Radiator Coolant Mixing
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The mixing of radiator coolant with transmission fluid can cause transmission failure, leading to loss of power, accidents, and costly repairs.
symptoms: Transmission slippage
loss of power
overheating
unusual noises
and difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Notification and Recall by Nissan
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Nissan's failure to notify owners and issue a recall for the known radiator and transmission defect has led to costly repairs, accidents, and safety risks.
symptoms: Owners were not informed of the potential defect
and Nissan did not issue a recall
leading to unexpected and costly repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated or flashing
airbags fail to deploy in an accident
passenger airbag activation light is intermittently signaling off
airbag light blinks and horn does not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall parts can lead to a delay in repairing the vehicle, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries due to faulty airbag systems.
symptoms: Part to do the recall repair is not yet available
manufacturer has exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can lead to the airbag system malfunctioning, which can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Passenger front seat sensor failed
airbag light constantly blinks and does not go off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can lead to the airbag system malfunctioning, which can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: VDC and slip light are constantly on when the battery has either died or has been disconnected
airbag light is constantly flashing and illuminated after the battery was disconnected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brake pedal to travel to the floor, leading to delayed or incomplete stopping, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels spongy or soft
the brake pedal travels to the floor
the vehicle does not stop immediately
the ABS and VDC warning lights are illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Overheating of the front brakes can cause the brakes to soften, leading to delayed or incomplete stopping, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brakes feel soft or spongy
the brakes smell after braking downhill
the brakes continuously soften when driving downhill.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Brake Pad and Rotor Wear
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature wear of brake pads and rotors can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to delayed or incomplete stopping, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pads wear out quickly
the rotors become grooved
the vehicle pulls to one side when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS and VDC systems can cause the warning lights to illuminate, leading to a loss of traction and stability, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ABS and VDC warning lights are illuminated
the vehicle's traction and stability are compromised.
